  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency autoprefixer to v7.1.5",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer\">autoprefixer</a> from <code>v7.1.4</code> to <code>v7.1.5</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>postcss/autoprefixer</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"715\">7.1.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/96c8cfb7714f4764c59f4130f718756a47c2fbf3\"><code>96c8cfb</code></a> Release 7.1.5 version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/fe790bdf63cc15628070cfe55e057071b610ebf3\"><code>fe790bd</code></a> Fix ::placeholder prefix for Edge</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/a2ef2a4a664888e6fae8b941e364014b676114d0\"><code>a2ef2a4</code></a> Fix common values in flex-direction</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/be2742b765044a7e53dcd58d9e12247ed519c613\"><code>be2742b</code></a> Update dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/ac37fce2d4f1ba4ee1901c1a40f91b594dfc173b\"><code>ac37fce</code></a> Clean up comments</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/a4444f73ffeaa6f0bad1169f2741fb8387045534\"><code>a4444f7</code></a> Bugfix reuse of global RegEx object. (#&#8203;918)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/2de3db86c53bb34f36ad3aa8966613175564b067\"><code>2de3db8</code></a> Update dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/6c8f609866e0fbac784835ce00dc5b9342495c4d\"><code>6c8f609</code></a> Fix typos (#&#8203;908)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/ebd01872461ace01ffdd5b9da31d209c281766b0\"><code>ebd0187</code></a> Fix other builder section</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer/commit/f343524885eb1cf516b31e43a1e9e17742a018f3\"><code>f343524</code></a> Link to Neutrino build tool integration in Readme (#&#8203;901)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
